{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"8c30b6a1-63cf-4ba1-b2e9-8bf86db1a2cd","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"2a9aec90-bb28-48ae-8264-b2b12fe84dcf","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"438392db-a930-4a04-9220-12c7f01ca373","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[3618,1420],"id":"8fe4efe6-7c17-40fa-9aff-50f593d620b4","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"from":"+15550100000","to":"={{ $json.phone || 'ONCALL_NUMBER' }}","message":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.twilio","typeVersion":1,"position":[3942,1420],"id":"151aa0c6-0066-40f0-964e-474f10d760d4","name":"Escalate Failure to Twilio","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Every Few Minutes\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — every 10 min. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Fetch Current Metrics","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"e1ebd13e-21cc-dca3-b6a6-91fdcdedc47d","name":"Note: Every Few Minutes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fetch Current Metrics\n\nGET https://api.example.com/v1/assets — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Severity Signals · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"6b486e35-7527-39e6-089e-e5927777dc91","name":"Note: Fetch Current Metrics"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Severity Signals\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compute a simple moving average and momentum signal\n\nNext: Grade Severity Tier","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"19df3c1c-2509-170c-88ce-bf87edf8da23","name":"Note: Compute Severity Signals"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Grade Severity Tier\n\nRoutes each item to one of 4 lanes: info, warning, critical + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Just Record (Info) · ②→ Warn Channel (Twilio) · ③→ Page Urgently (Slack) · ④→ Archive Unscored","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"073c5d85-8f7b-9103-3203-4bf181d516ac","name":"Note: Grade Severity Tier"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Just Record (Info)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Tier Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,40],"id":"d128d1bb-632e-b78b-5cbe-205a234acdfd","name":"Note: Just Record (Info)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Warn Channel (Twilio)\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Tier Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"862e564b-6e3f-eb03-413e-4a0773f275b9","name":"Note: Warn Channel (Twilio)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Page Urgently (Slack)\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Tier Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1000],"id":"f2ecfa24-2873-e6bb-b9c2-fbd2015c9b8d","name":"Note: Page Urgently (Slack)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Unscored\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Tier Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,1480],"id":"f04b9557-2d8d-de43-da8c-8cb2fac8ef25","name":"Note: Archive Unscored"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Tier Outcomes\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty price","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"e62b334c-c7ce-c1d9-c082-04a65f43c64a","name":"Note: Merge Tier Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty price\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"372dde29-360e-a724-4728-4049e694e481","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty price"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Send Summary to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"a6d7445a-c630-7066-f4e9-9377703729a7","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"04f0e273-01ed-d890-ea1b-034319ae837f","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Twilio","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,1540],"id":"2a826230-694d-462c-9b0b-9685d76e28af","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Twilio\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,1540],"id":"281d93b4-f872-b620-530f-e3f3a9bd24bf","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Twilio"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Alert on spend with HTTP / REST API and Twilio\n\n**Pattern:** Threshold Monitoring · **Level:** Core · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nAlert on spend with HTTP / REST API and Twilio. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual price alerts is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nEvery Few Minutes → Fetch Current Metrics → Compute Severity Signals → Grade Severity Tier → Just Record (Info) → Merge Tier Outcomes → Guard Non-Empty price → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to threshold monitoring without manual effort\n- Anyone automating price alerts in finance\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Scales without extra headcount\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2; Twilio SID + token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"d74d02f9-59cd-8990-6bc8-bfeeb7cf1132","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"28ef9676-069e-6513-180e-1ef611e03770","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your price alerts process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"d9c5b82f-95ea-0c37-3bcc-51738166ca6a","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Every Few Minutes":{"main":[[{"node":"Fetch Current Metrics","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fetch Current Metrics":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Severity Signals","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Severity Signals":{"main":[[{"node":"Grade Severity Tier","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Grade Severity Tier":{"main":[[{"node":"Just Record (Info)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Warn Channel (Twilio)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Page Urgently (Slack)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Archive Unscored","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Just Record (Info)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Warn Channel (Twilio)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Page Urgently (Slack)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Unscored":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Tier Outcomes":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty price","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty price":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Twilio","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"f1fbc17e-531a-46dc-a7fb-0a556d65827d","id":"FDX08901"}